                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-70-defend615 t18030420-70-punish377"></join>
               Fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Heath.</p>
